1. *Potrebni* su nam novi stolovi. (We need new tables.)

2. Oni su *potrebna* oprema za rad. (They are necessary equipment for work.)

3. On je *potrebno* pronašao rešenje. (He had to find a solution.)

4. *Potrebno* je popraviti krov. (The roof needs to be repaired.)

5. Mi smo *potrebni* da završimo zadatak. (We are needed to finish the task.)

6. *Potrebne* su nam nove ideje. (We need new ideas.)